LLB Internship Programme.eligibility:
Indian students who have completed :

   1. 2nd year of study and have written the examination to enter 3rd year or; 
   1. studying in the 3rd year of three-year degree course or;
   1. the students studying in the 4th year who have written examination to enter 5th year or; 
   1. studying in the 5th year of five-year degree course.
